org.opendaylight.yang.gen.v1.urn.opendaylight.host.tracker.rev140624

Interface Host

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.opendaylight.yang.gen.v1.urn.opendaylight.address.tracker.rev140617.AddressNodeConnector, org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.DataContainer, org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.DataObject
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    HostNode

    public interface Host
extends org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.DataObject, org.opendaylight.yang.gen.v1.urn.opendaylight.address.tracker.rev140617.AddressNodeConnector
    List of addresses and attachment points

    This class represents the following YANG schema fragment defined in module host-tracker-service 

     grouping host {
     list addresses {
         key "id"
         leaf id {
             type uint64;
         }
         leaf mac {
             type mac-address;
         }
         leaf ip {
             type ip-address;
         }
         leaf vlan {
             type vlan-id;
         }
         leaf first-seen {
             type int64;
         }
         leaf last-seen {
             type int64;
         }
     }
     leaf id {
         type host-id;
     }
     list attachment-points {
         key "tp-id"
         leaf tp-id {
             type tp-id;
         }
         leaf-list tp-ref {
             type tp-ref;
         }
         leaf corresponding-tp {
             type tp-ref;
         }
         leaf active {
             type boolean;
         }
         uses tp-attributes;
     }
 }
    The schema path to identify an instance is host-tracker-service/host
